markdownRemark.html: Located at the foot of the Gran Vía you find this spectacular Renaissance cathedral with its baroque touches, which stands out for having 5 naves. You can enjoy the wonderful view of the Royal Chapel and the Cathedral.

frontmatter.title: Capilla Real
frontmatter.description: Capilla Real - Located at the foot of the Gran Vía you find this spectacular Renaissance cathedral with its baroque touches, which stands out for having 5 naves. You can enjoy the wonderful view of the Royal Chapel and the Cathedral.
frontmatter.price: The price is 5.00 euro for the cathedral and 5.00 euro for the Royal Chapel.
